description:
Eat Clean - Stay Lean!

In this course you will learn:

  • What clean eating is and the real nutrition behind it
  • How to eat to feel your best and have the most energy
  • How to shop, super-foods, antioxidants and what to stock in your fridge and pantry
  • A 14 day meal plan and menus to get you started. I've included a meal plan for vegetarians and vegans as well
  • 14 day journal
  • Daily motivational videos to guide and encourage you along the way!
  • 100 recipes with nutritional information
  • 50 recipe demonstration videos
  • There is a FAQ section, and as a bonus
  • 10 habits and tips for a healthy life
title: 14 Day Healthy Diet Plan!
